{
  "texts": [
    "In the down-aligned case, the numbers are 64 (EW), 45 (colliders) and 15 (flavor).",
    "The sole (slight) exception to this trend is C(1)[3333] quqd, whose bound in the down-alignment limit is 2.2 TeV.",
    "To this purpose, an interesting indication is obtained by identifying the relative weights for the WCs associated to specific tree-level mediators, as discussed recently in[59] in the U(3) 5 symmetric case."
